{"tid":1855213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來中環四季酒店又名望北樓","createTime":"2020-02-01T03:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T17:45:27.000Z","uid":104804,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab1b3859ca5c78747235ce1aa3ed87d0596336b","tid":1855213,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:26:27.000Z","msg":"「望北樓」內地富豪有三大共通點：一、持香港身份證或外國護照；二、在內地惹上「麻煩」，來港暫避風頭；三、自信「麻煩」未到最嚴重地步，尚有轉圜餘地，不捨得放棄內地生意而遠走高飛。「望北樓」之關鍵在一個「望」字。<br />\n<br />\n中環四季酒店聚居着大批因故滯港的內地富豪，他們天天盼着自己在內地的麻煩可獲解決，那便能夠早日北歸，所以這幢酒店又被戲稱為「望北樓」。<br />\n<br />\n武肺咪去香港避下<br />\n有咩事咪直接去歐美<br />\n反正大把錢"},{"pid":"33d2325b674bd7a4042b1d63d40e91f29e505549","tid":1855213,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ef444d2f6f7d6de9da7bdc8bd7e8b0fa43f6e3","tid":1855213,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e076b6ec58d5f61322dd65fa8dbb02593955ddd","tid":1855213,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:21:16.000Z","msg":"唔封關等權貴黎香港等走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d8c9b3fe5032b52c1df9658629e0c99e5a9bfb","tid":1855213,"uid":74163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:23:42.000Z","msg":"真心咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8de89959d18b615eeecc56536b2ead872f0f11","tid":1855213,"uid":1224,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:28:09.000Z","msg":"當逃犯引渡條例生效，有一個行業影響很大，就是那些五星級酒店，他們將會損失一批長期大客，因為在香港的逃犯是不會買樓，甚至連租樓也不會，他們會長期租住酒店，令到那些酒店有一個外號，叫做「望北樓」，就是北望神州，有家歸不得的意思。"},{"pid":"e77bcd6225f3036bc66daf566485e58dac1dcf74","tid":1855213,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:33:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ed94b01cc7a61b7ce76f101a4564c72beb00801c","tid":1855213,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59d8c9b3fe5032b52c1df9658629e0c99e5a9bfb","tid":1855213,"uid":74163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:23:42.000Z","msg":"真心咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:35:25.000Z","msg":"中招果個鄧生原來大陸高官"},{"pid":"4451d4500ad670ad5bcaa7f4bc328139bc882825","tid":1855213,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:40:19.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"f65539b344c9619054921dc1205eb662d8a1453c","tid":1855213,"uid":150523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:45:27.000Z","msg":"肖建華都係呢度比人綁返上去"}]}